{
  "stem": "3380.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This is the second time what I had dreamt that my mother came and she said that, don't worry about.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You-- they are [? surrendered. ?] They're going to take you out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Don't worry that you will get killed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We start marching.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we start marching [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] for days and days and days.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't know how long.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I remember-- in that process of march, I remember that-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in march I find out also that President Roosevelt died, and they were celebrating his death.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I know that he died-- that was the 12th of April, 1945, if I'm not mistaken.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I think so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "This I do remember, you see, that they were celebrating now actually the-- that the war going to go on their side.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we start marching.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We didn't know where we're going, how we're going, what we're going.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the shooting was going on the same day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "By the end, I didn't know where the Russians are, where the Germans are, where the American.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I know that the Germans are watching us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we used to sleep in the forest.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And one time-- that was the 8th of May-- I mean, now I know, at that time, I didn't know-- they released all the prisoners, and they gave them packages from the Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But the Jewish prisoners they kept separate, and they let everybody go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After that, they took us into a farm-- to a farmhouse.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They put us in in a barn.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, that was something unusual, because we used to sleep in the forest, you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They used to watch us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They didn't care if the rain or shine.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
